title: MisterMusic Show 290 NEW indie,alternative,rock radio
description:
MisterMusic Show  290 - (2 hours) 192 kbps MP3



New music on this week's show by The Pixies, Snakadaktal, and Dum Dum Girls.
Plus a big alternative rock hit from early Feb 1994 is the 'Oldie of the Week'.

2 hours of new indie and alternative music mixed with classic hits from the past.



The MisterMusic Show is broadcast weekly and heard globally on RockXS internet radio.


---------------------------------------------------------------------------------

For recorded podcasts of the MisterMusic show, visit his podcast page http://mistermusicshow.com/
Shows are updated there first every Sunday.
Or you can google search  mistermusicshow  (spelled as one word) and you'll find it.
